# ─── Required ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your API key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ─── Optional: Vercel AI Gateway ────────────────────────────────────────────
# If you deploy to Vercel, you can remove ANTHROPIC_API_KEY and instead
# run `vercel link` → `vercel env pull` to get OIDC-based auth automatically.
# Then update app/api/analyze/route.ts to use AI Gateway model strings:
#   model: 'anthropic/claude-opus-4.5'   (via @ai-sdk/gateway)
